BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 153.6 465 Td (they go to Rainbow Bridge.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 132.0 433 Td (There are meadows and hills for all) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 132.0 417 Td (our special friends so they can run) Tj ET
